amily: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:62.2000pt;"><td width="50" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1.33px 1.33px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; background-color: transparent;"><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 10pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">6</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p></td><td width="305" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1.33px 1.33px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; background-color: transparent;"><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 10pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">第六次课 &nbsp;大学生爱情心理与调试</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 72.9pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">（课本第八章）</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 10pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p></td><td width="70" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1.33px 1.33px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; background-color: transparent;"><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 10pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:28.3500pt;"><td width="355" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1.33px 1.33px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; background-color: transparent;" colspan="2"><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 10pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">考核方式</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p></td><td width="70" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1.33px 1.33px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; background-color: transparent;"><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 10pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">论文</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:28.3500pt;"><td width="355" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1.33px 1.33px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; background-color: transparent;" colspan="2"><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 10pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">合 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;计</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p></td><td width="70" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1.33px 1.33px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; background-color: transparent;"><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 10pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">12</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><h1 style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 28.1pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">五、教学方法与手段</span>&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></h1><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">本课程在教学过程中，每讲内容均采用讲练结合的方法。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（一）教学方法</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">1.本课程既有心理知识的传授，心理活动的体验，还有心理调适技能的训练等，是集知识、体验和训练为一体的综合课程。课程要注重理论联系实际，注重培养学生实际应用能力。</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">2.课程要充分发挥师生在教学中的主动性和创造性。教师要尊重学生的主体性，充分调动学生参与的积极性，开展课堂互动活动，避免单向的理论灌输和知识传授。</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">3.课程要采用理论与体验教学相结合、讲授与训练相结合的教学方法，如课堂讲授、案例分析、小组讨论、心理测试、团体训练、情境表演、角色扮演、体验活动等。</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 27pt; layout-grid-mode: char;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（二）教学手段</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">1.多媒体教学。教师可充分利用多媒体，运用体验式、案例</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">教学、情景模拟等方法，使学生直观感受教学内容，掌握学习内容，转变学生观念，提高学生的就业能力。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">2.充分发挥学生骨干的作用，开展延续性教学活动。学生可以不受时间、地点的限制，自觉地、自主地进一步实践本课程的教学内容。</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><h1 style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 27pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">六、课程的实践教学环节</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></h1><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">在互动体验式的教学理念的指导下，重视培养大学生的自我心理调适能力。开展心理测试、心理网站建设、心理健康节活动、校园心理情景剧、心理培训、专题心理讲座、个体心理咨询和团体心理的辅导等多种实践教学活动，有效提升学生的心理自助能力，促进学生的心理成长。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><h1 style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 27pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">七、考核方式：</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></h1><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">改变以往单一的考核形式，加重过程性考核在学生学业成绩的权重系数，其构成如下：学期成绩</span>=平时成绩（作业/考勤/实践性活动）（40%）+ 期末考试成绩（60%）。</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><h1 style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 27pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">八、参考书目</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></h1><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">【</span>1】黄希庭.心理学导论.人民教育出版社.1991年</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">【</span>2】张春兴.现代心理学.上海人民出版社.1994年</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">【</span>3】樊富珉.大学生心理素质教程.北京出版社.2002年</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">【</span>4】段鑫星、赵玲.大学生心理健康教育.科学出版社.2003年</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">【</span>5】孔燕等.微笑成长--大学生心理健康教育案例.安徽人民出版社.2004年</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">【</span>6】戴维</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;">•</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">迈尔斯</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;">.社会心理学.人民邮电出版社.2006年</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt;"></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin-top: 21px; margin-bottom: 21px;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>					</p>', '0', '1526861340', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `dk_article` (`id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `subtitle`, `thumb`, `video`, `content`, `note`, `create_at`, `enabled`, `sort`, `click`, `istj`, `istwtj`, `link`) VALUES
(54, 8, '黄河水院阳光心理联合会第十届换届大会成功举办', '', '', NULL, '<p>					</p><p><br/></p><h1 style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体">黄河水院阳光心理联合会第十届换届大会成功举办</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></h1><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">11月8日下午4点，黄河水院阳光心理联合会第十届换届大会在三号实训楼水利报告厅顺利召开。学生处处长谷献晖、副处长王国英、心理健康教育科主任郭豪杰及各院系心理指导老师出席本次大会。</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt;"><img title="1526632466866819.png" alt="image.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-18/1526632466866819.png"/><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">会上王处长和郭老师正式公布了心联会第十届干部任命名单，第十届干部团队正式履任。第九届心联会主席刘鹏做了工作汇报与总结，他鼓励第十届干部团队不忘初心开拓进取，为心联会带来更好的明天。第十届心联会主席王震携全体心联会成员庄重宣誓，致力于我校大学生心理健康教育工作。第十届干部代表席慧慧发言，她表示一定会继承上届干部不怕辛苦努力奉献的精神，并将提升自我积极创新，努力为学校的心理健康教育工作做出更大的贡献。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">大会最后谷处长总结发言，谷处长首先对第九届干部的付出表示感谢，对第十届干部的履任表示祝贺。谷处长指出心联会在学校的心理健康教育工作中发挥了重要的作用，为提高我校大学生心理健康水平和综合素质能力做出了卓越的贡献，换届大会的成功召开标志着责任的传承，希望第十届干部能够发挥学生社团自我管理、服务学生的职能，一方面实现自我的锻炼和成长，另一方面也要服务全校学生，帮助更多同学摆脱心理困惑走进阳光生活。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">阳光心理联合会是服务于全校学生的公益性组织，长期以来协助心理健康教育科老师开展心理健康教育工作，组织心理素质拓展活动、举办现场心理咨询心理测评与沙盘展示活动、开展微笑图片征集活动、大学生自信风采大赛等等丰富多彩形式多样的心理健康教育活动，为普及心理健康知识，提高我校大学生整体心理素质做出了卓越贡献，得到学校领导、老师及同学们的一致好评。此次心联会换届大会的成功召开，为学校今后心理健康教育活动的顺利开展奠定了坚实的基础。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>					</p>', '0', '1478880000', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(5, 1, '心理健康教育中心简介', '', '/upload/2018-04-16/5ad4135b2d51a.doc', NULL, '<p>					</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 22pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:黑体">心理</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 22pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:黑体">健康教育</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 22pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:黑体">中心简介</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 22pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:黑体"></span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;">◆中心简介</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.1pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">心理健康教育中心是面向全校学生实施心理健康教育和开展心理咨询服务的专业机构。中心隶属于学生工作部（处），依托各院系，采用专兼结合的工作体制，全面开展教学、测量、咨询、研究、培训工作。中心内设个别咨询室和办公室</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">聘有校内外专家、心理学专业人员为广大同学提供专业权威的发展性心理咨询服务，帮助同学们解决在成长过程中遇到的心理困惑和问题。</span>&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;">◆指导思想</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">中心所有工作的开展以全体学生的健康成长和全面发展为中心；以预防为本，发展为主，治疗为辅为原则；以提高学生的心理素质，适应未来社会的挑战为目标。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">◆</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:黑体">求助方式</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">学生可以采取的咨询方式有：电话咨询、电子信箱咨询、面对面咨询、团体咨询等。在这些咨询方式中，面对面咨询效果最好，其次是电话咨询和电子信箱咨询。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.1pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:宋体">工作时间：</span></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">周一至周五</span> &nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">上午</span>8：00——12：00</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 29.4px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 165pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">下午</span>3：00——6：00（夏令时）</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 29.4px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 165pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2：30——5：30</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">冬</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">令时）</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.1pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:宋体">工作地点：</span></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">中心位于</span>5号教学楼</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">一楼</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">东头，包括</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">预约</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">咨询室（</span>JX5101）、办公室（JX510</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">8</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">）、心理咨询室（</span>JX510</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span>JX510</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">3</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体">）、心理宣泄室（</span>JX5105）、心理测验室和箱庭治疗室（JX5107）等。为广大学生配备了放松躺椅、智能身心反馈训练仪、心理自助服务一体机、智能互动宣泄仪、心理测量软件等仪器和设备。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.1pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:宋体">预约电话：</span></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">0371-23658236</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;">◆服务宗旨</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">增进学生心理健康，培养学生健全人格，帮助学生解决成长过程中遇到的心理问题，发展学生个人潜能，促进学生全面、健康发展。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;">◆服务对象</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">向全体全日制在校学生免费开放。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;">◆服务内容</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">1.开设心理健康教育必修课，心理选修课、专题讲座和报告、心理行为训练和团体培训，传授心理调试方法，引导和帮助学生树立心理健康意识；</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">2.开展心理咨询活动，帮助学生处理好环境适应、自我管理、学习成才、人际交往、交友恋爱、求职择业、人格发展和情绪调节等方面的困惑，及时进行危机干预；</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">3.开展心理健康普查与心理测量，建立心理档案，帮助学生更好地认识自己，做出正确的自我评价和自我期望；</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">4.编印心理健康教育宣传资料，开设心理健康教育网页，宣传普及心理健康知识；</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">5.进行大学生心理问题与心理健康教育的调查研究，为学校改进和加强学生工作提供信息服务、对策和建议。</span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;">◆服务承诺</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">真诚、</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">保密、</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">尊重、</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">热情</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 6.66px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family:宋体">心理咨询中心以服务学生为根本出发点，以培养健康心理为奋斗宗旨，热情欢迎广大同学走进中心，畅谈心事，共述美好人生！</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>					</p>', '0', '1527177600', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(74, 9, '水资源工程系举办心理素质拓展活动', '', '', NULL, '<p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 23px;"><strong><span style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">水资源工程系举办心理素质拓展活动</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 23px;"><img title="1526964359609386.jpg" alt="20160617173924659001.jpg" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526964359609386.jpg"/><strong><span style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(81, 69, 69); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;">4</span></strong><strong><span style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(81, 69, 69); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;">月28日上午，系心理素质拓展活动在东南体育场举行，此次活动由学生处主办，院阳光心理联合会承办，系分会协办，学生处卫聪聪老师、陈志冉老师、朱孟昀老师担任活动指导，系副辅导员侯礼婷系14级90名大一新生参加活动。此次拓展训练采用分组PK的形式进行，90位学生分成4组，一次体验“盲人方阵”和“有轨电车”两个项目。同学们都积极地参与到活动中，各小组在每个项目开始前都会响亮的喊出自己的口号，凝练小组士气，激发组员的竞争意识。每个同学都积极出力，贡献自己的聪明才智，力争所在组获得好成绩。通过此次素质拓展训练活动同学们认识到团队活动中，团结协作，相互配合的重要性。活动结束后，各小组指导老师带领大家对今天体验的活动进行思考，让大家对拓展训练的感受和收获进行了分享总结，同学们表示这种活动非常有意义，还建议挑战其他的拓展项目，同时也希望学院、系部能够提供更多的机会让同学们以团队形式参加，发挥团队的智慧和力量。</span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p></p>', '0', '1430150400', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(75, 9, '我校第二届素质拓展大赛成功举办', '', '', NULL, '<h1 style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">我校第二届素质拓展大赛成功举办</span></span></strong></h1><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1526966323622863.jpg" alt="QQ图片20180523132427.jpg" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526966323622863.jpg"/><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;开幕式</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><img title="1526966336611524.jpg" alt="QQ图片20180523132417.jpg" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526966336611524.jpg"/><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">团队展示</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><img title="1526966349195638.jpg" alt="QQ图片20180523132401.jpg" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526966349195638.jpg"/><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">有轨电车</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><img title="1526966365656974.jpg" alt="QQ图片20180523132406.jpg" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526966365656974.jpg"/><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">踊跃硫酸池</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><img title="1526966382249799.jpg" alt="QQ图片20180523132401.jpg" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526966382249799.jpg"/><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">无敌风火轮</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: center;"><img title="1526966398693822.jpg" alt="QQ图片20180523132351.jpg" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526966398693822.jpg"/><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">穿越电网</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">4月22日，学生处在西北五环体育场素质拓展基地举办以</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">熔炼团队、超越自我</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">为主题的第二届素质拓展大赛，此次大赛分为团队展示、竞赛项目和团队分享三个环节。学生处处长谷献晖、校团委书记刘许亮、宣传部副部长姚芬、体育部副主任蔡寄平、学生处副处长王国英等出席大赛开幕式并担任团队展示环节评委，来自12个院系的16支代表队参赛。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">上午8点开幕式准时开始，谷处长为大赛致辞。谷处长为大家介绍了我校素质拓展活动基地及素质拓展的来源及意义，并介绍了自2013年以来，我校开展素质拓展活动所取得的成效。谷处长希望各位同学认真领会素质拓展的内涵，在活动中提高自己的素质品质，把自己培养成符合当今时代需求的综合素质高技能人才。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">团队展示环节现场欢声笑语、气氛热烈，活动中，16支参赛队激情昂扬、朝气蓬勃地展示了本队的队名、队旗、队形、队训和队歌等，充分展现了当代大学生良好的精神风貌。竞赛项目环节，参赛队伍限时挑战</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">穿越电网</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">无敌风火轮</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">踊跃硫酸池</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">有轨电车</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">等4个拓展项目。团队分享环节，每位参赛选手用一句话概括了参加此次大赛的感想和收获。赛场上，选手们激情飞扬、勇往直前，他们用团队奉献和团队协作创下了一项项优异成绩，向同学们展示了素质拓展的强大力量。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">大赛历时一天，经过激烈比拼，最终水利工程学院“荣耀队</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、土木与交通工程学院</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">烈焰队</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">获得一等奖，机械工程学院</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">先锋队</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">等4支参赛队伍获得二等奖，自动化工程系</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">奔跑的蜗牛队</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">等6支参赛队伍获得三等奖，财经系</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">以梦为马队</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">等4支参赛队伍获得优秀奖。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">本次大赛是我校第四届心理素质教育系列活动的重要内容，此次大赛的成功举办能增强同学们对素质拓展活动的认识，对于提高我校学生的心理健康水平和综合素质能力具有积极作用。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p></p>', '0', '1492790400', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(76, 9, '校首届心理素质拓展大赛成功举办', '', '', NULL, '<p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 23px;"><strong><span style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">校首届心理素质拓展大赛成功举办</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 23px;"><img title="1526966650527338.png" alt="20160617175955868001.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526966650527338.png"/><strong><span style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;">“春晚绿野秀，岩高白云屯”。5月7日，我校西北五环体育场一片欢声笑语，来自全校12个院（系）的200余名同学斗志昂扬、情绪高涨地参加了校首届心理素质拓展大赛。</span></p><p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">上午</span>9时，开幕式准时举行。学生处副处长王国英、体育部副主任蔡寄平、体育教研室主任张亚廷、学生处心理健康教育科主任郭豪杰、校素质拓展指导老师卫聪聪、王超出席大赛开幕式并担任大赛团队展示环节评委。开幕式由学生处朱孟昀老师主持，各参赛队伍指导老师出席开幕式并全赛程跟队指导。</span></p><p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">开幕式上，学生处副处长王国英为大赛致辞，王处长提出我校从</span>2013年以来不断完善素质拓展硬件设施和软件建设，实现从无到有，从有到优的跨越，建成涵盖“毕业墙”、“盲目障碍”、“信任背摔”、“硫酸池”等8个拓展项目的大学生心理素质拓展基地，通过举行心理素质拓展活动致力提高大学生的心理素质和心理健康水平。本次大赛将心理素质拓展训练以比赛形式纳入我校，不仅能够激发和推动我校大学生心理健康教育，更重要的是能让学生在亲身参与的过程中，提高自我调整心理状态的主动性。</span></p><p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">本次大赛分为团队展示、竞赛项目、团队分享三个环节，团队展示环节现场气氛热烈，</span>16支参赛代表队激情昂扬、朝气蓬勃地展示了本队的队名、队旗、队形、队训和队歌等，充分展现了当代大学生良好的精神风貌；竞赛项目环节，参赛队伍限时挑战“穿越电网”、“无敌风火轮”、“踊跃硫酸池”、“有轨电车”四个拓展项目；团队分享环节每位参赛选手用一句话概括了此次大赛自己的感想和收获。大赛历时一天，赛场上选手们激情飞扬、勇往直前，他们把热情和汗水留在了赛场，把友谊和进步收进了行囊。经过激烈比拼，最终水利工程学院齐猛队、测绘工程学院老司机队获得一等奖、信息工程系先锋队等4支参赛队伍获得二等奖、国际教育学院青春队等6支参赛队伍获得三等奖，旅游系梦想队等4支参赛队伍获得优秀奖。</span></p><p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">本次大赛以</span>“培养健康心理，拓展美丽人生”为主题，是本学期第三届心理素质教育系列活动的一项重要内容，活动目的是提高我校大学生综合素质，拓展大学生个性潜力。此次心理素质拓展大赛的成功举办是我校心理健康教育及素质能力教育的又一创新，对于培养具有高素质能力的高等技术专业性人才具有十分重要的意义。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p></p>', '0', '1462550400', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(77, 9, '自动化系举办心理素质拓展活动', '', '', NULL, '<p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 23px;"><strong><span style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">自动化系举办心理素质拓展活动</span></span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 23px;"><img title="1526966866497071.jpg" alt="20160617173506945001.jpg" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526966866497071.jpg"/><strong><span style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(71, 71, 71); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 29px; text-indent: 37px;"><strong><span style="background: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(81, 69, 69); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;">4月9日上午，自动化系心理素质拓展活动在东南体育场举行，此次活动由学生处主办，院阳光心理联合会承办，系分会协办，学生处霍卫红老师、董新法老师、朱孟昀老师担任活动指导，系副书记鄢彬彬、辅导员李翔老师、系心理健康指导老师朱海英以及系14级100名大一新生参加活动。活动开始前，鄢书记发表讲话，要求全体参训学员全身心的投入，鼓励同学们在活动中秉承友谊第一，比赛第二的精神，在活动中发扬团结友爱、互帮互助的精神。此次拓展训练采用小组对抗、项目积分的形式进行，通过限时挑战“穿越电网”和“有轨电车”两个项目，使同学们在体验中领悟“熔炼团队、超越自我”的内涵，在分享中感悟“思索在某些时候比行动更重要”的真谛，并通过这次活动使同学们认识到团队协作的重要性。素质拓展训练活动结束后，各团队对拓展训练的感受和收获进行了“一句话总结”，同学们还建议挑战其他的拓展项目，同时也希望学院、系部能够提供更多的机会让同学们以团队形式参加，发挥团队的智慧和力量。</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p></p>', '0', '1428508800', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(78, 8, '面对面，心联心——我校举办现场心理测评、咨询与沙盘展示活动', '', '', NULL, '<h1 style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">面对面，心联心</span>——我校举办现场心理测评、咨询与沙盘展示活动</span></strong></h1><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">阳光明媚，春风拂面。我校</span></span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">2018年“</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">现场心理测评、咨询与沙盘展示</span></span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">”活动于4月17日</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">下午在青年大道举行，心理健康教育中心郭豪杰老师在现场为同学们的心理状况答疑解惑。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1526967444793820.png" alt="20180418101732530001.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967444793820.png"/><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1526967455991380.png" alt="20180418101732960002.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967455991380.png"/><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; text-indent: 40px;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">本次活动的测评部分由校阳光心理联合会负责，现场问卷施测人员进行提前培训，使他们了解问卷的结构、问卷目的和问卷结果解释。现象测评中，同学们可以通过心理抗压能力、性格特征、职业潜能、手机依赖、气质、情绪、智商等问卷测试，使我校大学生了解自身特点，发现自身可能存在的心理困惑。对问卷或者自身心理有任何困惑的同学，通过和心理咨询师面对面交流，了解自身问题，评估心理健康状况。现场中很多同学对</span></span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;">“沙盘游戏”感兴趣，向老师预约了体验时间，从沙盘中了解自我，了解潜意识。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; text-indent: 40px;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">此次</span></span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;">“</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">心理测试、咨询与沙盘展示活动</span></span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;">”是我校“大学生心理健康教育活动”的一部分，通过活动的举办，让心理咨询和心理测评走进学生，让学生走近心理老师，用科学有效的方法综合评价自我，及时发现自身问题，</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">提高心理保健意识。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: center;"><img title="1526967480690325.png" alt="20180418101732255003.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967480690325.png"/><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p></p>', '0', '1523894400', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(79, 8, '手拉手 心联心 欢庆新年', '', '', NULL, '<h1 style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">手拉手</span> <span style="font-family: 宋体;">心联心</span> <span style="font-family: 宋体;">欢庆新年</span></span></strong></h1><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; text-indent: 40px;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">寒冷冬日，热情似火。为增强社团之间的友谊，加强交流与合作，校阳光心理联合会、诚信自强联合会和大学生自律委员会于</span>2018年1月8日晚7点，在大学生活动中心举办了联谊晚会。在老师的支持下，经过各方同学们的努力筹备，近四个小时的联谊晚会获得圆满成功。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1526967715273963.png" alt="20180109145311820001.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967715273963.png"/><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; text-indent: 40px;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">晚会在委婉动听的歌曲《江南》中拉开帷幕，动人的歌曲，感人肺腑的朗诵，以及令人欢笑的小品，博得了观众的阵阵掌声，由大学生自律委员会带来的口技《</span>BJR》让在座的各位观众惊叹不已。三方社团的主席分别进行了三次抽奖环节以及游戏环节，游戏环节中大家笑声不断。不知不觉联谊晚会接近尾声，大家在欢快的交谈中互相了解，建立了深厚的友谊。整场晚会的编排新颖、节目形式不拘一格、节目内容丰富多彩，展示了我校三大社团的风采，体现了当代大学生青春向上、积极进取的风貌。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span><img title="1526967735296874.png" alt="20180109145311802002.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967735296874.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span><img title="1526967753537878.png" alt="20180109145311214003.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967753537878.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span><img title="1526967771148585.png" alt="20180109145311118004.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967771148585.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span><img title="1526967791430892.png" alt="20180109145312247005.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967791430892.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span><img title="1526967811970511.png" alt="20180109145312479006.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967811970511.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span><img title="1526967828747896.png" alt="20180109145312666007.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526967828747896.png"/></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; text-indent: 40px;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">这次联谊晚会的成功举办，加强了三方社团各个干事的交流，交换了彼此的工作经验，进一步拉近了情感，为日后的工作筑建了桥梁，增进了大一新生之间的沟通，丰富了校园文化，展现了大学丰富多彩的生活。</span></span></p><p></p>', '0', '1515340800', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `dk_article` (`id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `subtitle`, `thumb`, `video`, `content`, `note`, `create_at`, `enabled`, `sort`, `click`, `istj`, `istwtj`, `link`) VALUES
(80, 8, '提高班级凝聚力，构建和谐大家庭——我校成功举办第九届心理主题班会大赛', '', '', NULL, '<p style="margin: 21px 0px; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 黑体; font-size: 29px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 黑体;">提高班级凝聚力，构建和谐大家庭</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 21px; text-align: right;"><strong><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 黑体; font-size: 21px; font-weight: bold;">——我校成功举办第九届心理主题班会大赛</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 21px; text-align: center;"><img title="1526968038919364.png" alt="20160617180533423001.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526968038919364.png"/><strong><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 黑体; font-size: 21px; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 43px;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">为加强和改进大学生心理健康，促进大学生思想道德素质建设和心理健康成长。</span>5月17日下午，由学生处主办，校阳光心理联合会承办的第九届心理主题班会决赛在学术报告厅拉开帷幕。</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">学生处副处长王国英、招生就业服务中心副主任马晓慧、水利工程学院党总支副书记楚万强、自动化工程系党总支副书记管欣、旅游系党总支书记樊建科、艺术系党总支书记来卫东、心理咨询中心主任郭豪杰担任本次比赛评委，各院（系）学生工作分管领导、心理指导老师和各班心理委员到现场观看。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 43px;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">学生处副处长王国英为大赛致辞，他说心理班会作为我校心理健康知识宣传的重要途径，有助于了解学生心理动态、普及心理健康知识、开展班级建设。为提高各班级的凝聚力，学生处特举办以</span>“增强班级凝聚力，构建和谐大家庭”为主题的心理班会活动。希望各院（系）学工人员以本次活动为契机积极探索大学生心理健康教育的新方法、新途径和新经验，秉承“只为成功找方法，不为失败找理由”的工作理念，继续推进我校的心理健康教育和心理安全工作。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 43px;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">决赛现场，</span>15个参赛班级代表各抒己见，展现了班会中同学们对如何增强班级凝聚力的看法和意见，</span><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">借助活动照片、视频和</span>PPT课件进行活动展示，从班会形式、班会意义以及取得的良好效果进行解说。最终，土木交通工程学院工程造价1505班和道桥1505班的解说员以饱满的热情、自信的解说赢得在场师生的阵阵掌声，荣获一等奖；机械工程学院模具1501班等5个班级荣获二等奖；环化系环测1502班等8个班级荣获三等奖。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 43px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">招生就业服务中心副主任马晓慧在比赛最后进行了精彩点评，她从班会策划多元化、现场解说技巧、</span>PPT制作技巧等方面，为同学们提出了行之有效的意见和建议，希望通过心理班会，同学们不仅仅获得心理知识的提升，更要以阳光积极的心态努力奋斗，提高社会适应能力。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 43px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">此次心理主题班会评选活动是本学期第三届心理素质教育系列活动的一项重要内容，从</span>3月中旬开始启动，共历时两个月。各院（系）组织在校班级以心理素质拓展活动，趣味游戏等形式开展心理主题班会活动，并举行院（系）心理主题班会评选。共推荐35个班级参加校心理主题班会评选初赛，最终15个班级进入最后的决赛。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 43px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">通过本次心理班会的开展，开拓了心理工作思路，增强了学生对心理知识的了解，促进了班级内部沟通，提高了班级凝聚力，促进了和谐校园建设。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p></p>', '0', '1463414400', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(7, 9, '我校“新相识，心相知”系列素质拓展活动圆满结束', '', '', NULL, '<p>					</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &amp;font-size: 24px;font-weight: 500;line-height: 26.4px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 20px"><span style="font-size: 24px;">我校“新相识，心相知”系列素质拓展活动圆满结束</span></h1><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-family: &amp;font-size: 14px;font-weight: 500;line-height: 15.4px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 20px"><br/></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 40px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 20px">2017年12月2日下午两点，校阳光心理联合会以“新相知，心相识”为主题的第五次，也是最后一次素质拓展活动在西北操场拉开序幕。此次活动由心理指导中心王超老师带领同学们进行，主要参与人员有2017级心联会成员和2016级干事。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px"><img width="553" height="369" src="/upload/image/2018-04-16/1523842053890832.png"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 40px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 20px"><span style="font-family:宋体">王超老师对本次活动进行了详细的介绍，带领同学们做了爬毕业墙时的主要肢体动作和热身运动，希望大家能够在爬毕业墙的时候注意安全和方式方法，在增强同学们之间的信任和团结的同时，提升了同学们做事的思考能力和解决方法。活动开始，同学们开始分工，有的同学组成人梯，有的同学则帮助别的同学进行爬毕业墙，下面做人梯的同学也不负重任和毕业墙上面的同学配合的特别好，第一次爬毕业墙并没有成功，在规定时间内全部成员没有全体都爬到毕业墙上，在老师的鼓励下，同学们没有放弃，高声喊起要来第二次，第一次的毕业墙也是给同学们的一次锻炼吧！在第二次的爬毕业墙同学们找到了一些技巧，虽然最后一名成员尝试几次都没能成功，但是经过全体同学的不懈努力，最终成功爬上毕业墙。为了检验同学们之间的信任和配合程度，第二次开展</span>“信任盲行”，这次的路程选择了比上次更惊险，从西北操场到鲲鹏山再到六号教学楼，一路上有台阶、有水池、有山体，路程崎岖不平，每组搭档相互帮助，最终全部安全回到教室进行《大学生心理素质量表》和《自我效能感量表》的后测，通过问卷填写和数据分析，检验同学们在素质拓展过程中的成长和收获。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px"><img width="553" height="369" src="/upload/image/2018-04-16/1523842054423386.png"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px"><img width="553" height="369" src="/upload/image/2018-04-16/1523842056497803.png"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px"><img width="553" height="369" src="/upload/image/2018-04-16/1523842057822375.png"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 40px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 20px">“新相识，心相知”系列素质拓展活动以信任盲行调查问卷的方式开始，以信任盲行、调查问卷的方式结束。在这系列素质拓展活动中增强了社团人员的凝聚力和内部的氛围，但更多的是让同学们学习到了人与人之间信任的建立，做事能力和学习技巧。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px"><img width="553" height="369" src="/upload/image/2018-04-16/1523842057638100.png"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>					</p>', '0', '1525222602', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(8, 8, '听从我心，无问西东————我校举办心理电影赏析活动', '', '', NULL, '<p>					</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><h1 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26.4px; font-weight: 500; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">听从我心，无问西东————我校举办心理电影赏析活动</span></h1><h2 style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 15.4px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></h2><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 21.33px; text-indent: 37.33px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="line-height: 28px; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18.66px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">为了普及心理健康知识，进一步落实心理健康教育的工作，在学校营造一种关注心理健康、懂得心理健康、重视心理健康的氛围，校阳光心理联合会举办的《无问西东》心理电影赏析活动于</span>2018年4月15日晚上7点，在教学楼2202拉开了序幕。校阳光心理联合会的干事以及各院系200余人参加了本次活动。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 21.33px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img width="553" height="311" src="/upload/image/2018-04-16/1523869552415542.png"/><span style="line-height: 28px; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18.66px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 21.33px; text-indent: 37.33px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="line-height: 28px; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18.66px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">电影开始前，由校阳光心理联合会的刘旭萌为大家简单介绍了一下电影的背景以及内容。电影所说，</span>“愿你在被打击时，记起你的珍贵，抵抗恶意；愿你在迷茫时，坚信你的珍贵；爱你所爱，行你所行，听从你心，无问西东。”这部电影描述的是四个不同时代的故事，却又紧紧相连，在电影中，每个时代，各有一群年轻的面庞，他们在各自的青春里成长，鲜衣怒马，风华正茂，然后在最好的年纪，面临最残酷的选择，他们每一个选择，都告诉我们一个答案。</span><span style="line-height: 28px; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18.66px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">大家看到搞笑画面的时候，开心地笑作一团；面对励志感人的画面，感性的女生眼中噙着泪花，是感动，更是对自己的鼓励；男生们深沉的目光中流露出的是坚毅。</span></span><span style="line-height: 28px; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18.66px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">电影闭幕，整个阶梯教室掌声雷鸣，有人发出感叹</span>--我们生于这个年代真是太好了，生于中国是在是幸运；也有人在议论--爱，是信仰，爱是感觉，并不是皮囊金钱名誉...</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 21.33px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img width="553" height="311" src="/upload/image/2018-04-16/1523869553737100.png"/><span style="line-height: 28px; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18.66px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 21.33px; text-indent: 37.33px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="line-height: 28px; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18.66px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">通过此次心理电影赏析活动的展开，不仅让学生体会到了，人在迷茫的年少时期，被点拨、被引导去叩问内心，做出适合自己的、真正想要去做的选择，不顾时代浪潮，不顾他人言语，不顾世俗评价，无问西东。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>					</p>', '0', '1523721600', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(23, 3, '关于举办第五届心理素质教育系列活动的通知', '', '', NULL, '<p>					</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img src="http://he.onways.cn/Public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif"/><a title="黄院学【2018】2号 关于举办第五届心理素质教育系列活动的通知 - 副本.doc" style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/upload/file/2018-05-02/1525222282768224.doc">黄院学【2018】2号 关于举办第五届心理素质教育系列活动的通知 .doc</a></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>					</p>', '0', '1525397403', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(73, 9, '梦想起航 并肩前行——校素质拓展队举行队伍培训', '', '', NULL, '<p style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 黑体; font-size: 29px;"><span style="font-family: 黑体;">梦想起航</span> </span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 黑体; font-size: 29px;"><span style="font-family: 黑体;">并肩前行</span></span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 黑体; font-size: 19px;">——校素质拓展队举行队伍培训</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: justify; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 43px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">“</span><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">三月金明柳絮飞，岸花堤草弄春时。”3月17日上午，我校西北体育场口号声声、掌声阵阵，校素质拓展队30余名成员队列整齐、英姿飒爽，兴致盎然、情绪高涨地参加素质拓展教练员队伍培训，培训由空降兵素质拓展培训基地教官担任指导，心理健康教育科科长郭豪杰到现场给队伍加油鼓劲。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: justify; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 43px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">本次培训是半封闭式培训，共2天，20个学时，目的是通过活动让学员们在</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">体验中学习，活动中成长</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。白天，学员们在教练员的指导下体验了</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">信任背摔</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">踊跃硫酸池</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">共同进步</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">无敌风火轮</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">翻越王屋山</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">十人九足</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">穿越电网</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">等7项素质拓展项目，通过体验式学习，学员们掌握了素质拓展活动流程、破冰技术、分享回顾的引导技术、活动与器材创新设计、团队学习等项目。晚上，教官组织学员们进行军事训练，并对白天的各项活动进行总结，休息的时候还组织大家进行才艺展示和趣味活动。在培训中大家都是非常认真地听教官的讲解并都把要点和注意事项牢记在心，学员们在活动中体验到了合作和分享的重要性。在培训中有位女同学受了伤，但依然轻伤不下火线，继续参加培训。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; text-align: justify; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 43px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">校素质拓展队于本学期由学生处选拔成立，共有30名大一新成员，分为男队和女队，学生处会继续对队伍进行培训，不断增强队员们的指导能力和创新能力，并进行考核，考核合格的队员将作为素质拓展教练对在校班级开展素质拓展培训活动。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<img title="1526964140264652.png" alt="20180320165812761001.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526964140264652.png"/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">信任背摔项目</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1526964151911596.png" alt="20180320165812237002.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526964151911596.png"/><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">无敌风火轮项目</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="1526964162208929.png" alt="20180320165812266003.png" src="/upload/image/2018-05-22/1526964162208929.png"/><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 楷体;">接受</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;">“奖励”</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p></p>', '0', '1521216000', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(16, 3, '关于认真做好2018年优秀应届毕业生评选工作的通知', '', '', NULL, '<p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt;"><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体">关于认真做好</span>2018年优秀应届毕业生</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt;"><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体">评选工作的通知</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">全校各院（系）：</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">根据河南省教育厅《关于评选河南省普通大中专学校优秀应届毕业生的通知》的文件精神</span>,现就我校推荐2018年河南省普通大中专学校优秀应届毕业生及黄河水院优秀应届毕业生评选工作的有关事项通知如下：</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:黑体">一、评选要求</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">请各院（系）根据省教育厅制定的《河南省普通大中专学校优秀应届毕业生评选工作实施办法》（见附件</span>1）、《黄河水院学生考核奖励办法》（详见《大学生学习生活指南》2017年版）及各院（系）实施细则的相关规定,结合本院（系）实际,按照“公开、公平、公正、择优”的原则,组织开展2018年优秀应届毕业生的推荐工作。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（一）严格标准，规范评选</span> </span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">评选优秀大学毕业生是一项原则性强、关注度高、影响面大的工作。各院（系）要高度重视，加强领导，认真组织，坚持标准，严格把关，保证质量。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">要坚持公开、公正、公平的原则，根据评选标准，综合考察评选对象各方面的一贯表现，广泛征求师生意见，增强评选工作透明度，确保评选质量，认真评选出广大师生认可的优秀应届毕业生。</span> </span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（二）树立典型，传播正能量</span> </span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">要通过开展评选工作，表彰先进，宣传典型，充分展示我校青年学子奋发向上、勇攀高峰的精神面貌，在大学生中广泛传播正能量，把评选工作提升为一次争先赶优、学习先进模范的教育活动，提高评选工作的教育效应和育人效果。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:黑体">二、评选对象和比例</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">评选对象为我校有正式学籍的全日制应届毕业生。评选比例为：省级优秀毕业生</span>3%（小数点后的数均舍去），校级优秀毕业生5%（小数点后的数均舍去）。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:黑体">三、评选标准</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">1. 具有坚定正确的政治方向，努力践行科学发展观，热爱社会主义祖国；拥护党和国家的路线、方针、政策，有较强的责任感和使命感。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">2. 遵守宪法和法律法规，模范遵守学生管理规定、学生行为准则，具有良好的道德品质和行为习惯。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">3. 学习勤奋，学业成绩优秀,德、智、体全面发展，百分制个人考核在班级排序中名列班级人数的前15%。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">4. 积极参加文体活动和其他公益活动，尊敬师长、关心同学，团结合作，师生反映良好。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">5. 在校期间获得校级（含校级）以上“三好学生”、“优秀学生干部”、“文明学生”等称号，获得国家奖学金、励志奖学金或国家级奖项，在有关重大活动中为学校争得荣誉的优先考虑。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">6.</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">在校期间创业的优先考虑，创业大学生所占比例不得低于最终评选人数的</span>10%。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:黑体">四、材料清单和上交时间</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（一）省级优秀毕业生</span></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">1. 《省级优秀毕业生推荐名单总表》（见附件2）纸质文档和电子文档，纸质文档一式2份。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">2. 《河南省大中专学校优秀应届毕业生审批表》（见附件4）纸质文档和电子文档，纸质文档一式2份，统一用A4纸正反面打印，做到内容真实，各项不得空缺。</span><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（表格位置不变）</span></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（二）校级优秀毕业生</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">1. 《校级优秀毕业生推荐名单总表》（见附件3）纸质文档和电子文档，纸质文档一式2份。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">2. 《黄河水利职业技术学院优秀应届毕业生审批表》（见附件5）纸质文档和电子文档，纸质文档一式2份，统一用A4纸打印，做到内容真实，各项不得空缺。</span><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（表格位置不变）</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（三）</span>2018年优秀应届毕业生先进事迹材料</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">各院（系）选报一名优秀应届毕业生的先进事迹材料，要求材料有故事性、启发意义，读后有感悟、收获；材料中的人物政治上可靠，充满正能量。（</span>1500字左右，打印稿和电子稿各一份，格式见附件6）。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（四）证明材料</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">参评学生在校期间的学习成绩单、两学年的班级百分制考核排名表、审批表涉及的主要荣誉证书复印件各一份。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">以上材料须经院（系）学生工作分管领导签字并加盖院（系）党总支公章，电子版通过办公自动化发送至学生处办公室和郭豪杰用户，纸质材料于</span></span><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;">3月16日17时前</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">报送至学生处</span>JX5108办公室。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">请各院（系）按期上报，所有数据项应准确无误，如出现错报、漏报等问题，不再补办证书。本通知的电子文档已通过校办公自动化系统传阅。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">联</span> <span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">系</span> <span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">人：郭豪杰</span> &nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">王超</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">联系电话：</span>23658236</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 126.4px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: -63.2pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">附件：</span>1. 河南省普通大中专学校优秀应届毕业生评选工作实施办法</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 79pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">2. 2018年省级优秀应届毕业生推荐名单总表</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 78.05pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">3. 2018年校级优秀应届毕业生推荐名单总表</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 78.05pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">4. 河南省普通大中专学校优秀应届毕业生审批表</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 78.05pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">5. 黄河水利职业技术学院优秀应届毕业生审批表</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 78.05pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">6. 优秀毕业生典型事迹材料模板</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img src="http://he.onways.cn/Public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif"/><a title="黄院学【2018】1号 关于认真做好2018年优秀应届毕业生评选工作的通知.doc" style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/upload/file/2018-04-18/1524040000183333.doc">黄院学【2018】1号 关于认真做好2018年优秀应届毕业生评选工作的通知.doc</a></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.6pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '1524040004', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
(22, 5, '我校举办心理健康手抄报大赛', '', '', NULL, '<p>					</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><h1 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26.4px; font-weight: 500; box-sizing: border-box;">我校举办心理健康手抄报大赛</h1><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-family: &amp;font-size: 14px;font-weight: 500;line-height: 15.4px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 20px"><br/></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">为了增强大学生对心理健康知识的认识和关注，提高心理健康水平，丰富课余生活，在全校范围内营造关注心理健康、懂得心理健康、重视心理健康健康的心理文化氛围，我校于</span>11月13日—11月30日期间组织开展了以“理性平和、健康心态”为主题的心理手抄报大赛。本次活动由我校学生工作部（处）主办，土木与交通工程学院承办。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-align: center;text-indent: 42.66px"><img width="554" height="416" src="/upload/image/2018-04-28/1524876283541718.png"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 37.33px; text-indent: 42.66px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong>土木与交通工程学院心理工作站认真进行初选</strong><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px">&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"> </span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">此次心理健康手抄报大赛，各院（系）十分重视，号召广大同学踊跃参与，截至</span>11月26日，共有来自全校各个院（系）的521幅作品参赛，其中水利工程学院266幅、测绘工程学院64幅、机械工程学院60幅、土木与交通工程学院52幅。11月27日上午，土木与交通工程学院党总支书记赵杰、副书记师军良、分团委书记戚亮、心理指导老师姚鹏、靳玉娟作为评审，从版面设计、内容、插图、字体和设计等方面对作品进行第一轮评审，选出120幅作品进入第二轮。11月29日下午，学生处副处长霍卫红、心理健康教育科科长郭豪杰、心理健康教育科王超和刘娟老师从作品的创意、版面图案、整体效果等方面进行终审，最终有80幅作品从中脱颖而出，自动化工程系电气1701班孙誉轩等10名同学获得一等奖，管理系跨境电商蒋方方等20名同学获得二等奖，水利工程学院水利管理1716班赵程栋等50名同学获得三等奖，获奖作品将以海报的形式在全校展示。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 37.33px; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img width="493" height="329" src="/upload/image/2018-04-28/1524876284772672.png"/><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 37.33px; text-indent: 42.66px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;学生处认真进行复选</span></strong></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 64px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 64px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px">&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312"><br/> </span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312"><br/> </span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"> </span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312"><br/> </span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">同学们在作品的创作中，感悟生命的精彩，追寻心中的梦想，用自己独特的视角、专属的色彩，描绘着心目中的</span>“理性平和、健康心态”，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">一幅幅作品诠释着心理健康教育的精髓。这些作品用细腻的文字分享着心理调适的方法，为同学传达心理健康的标准，讲述心理健康的有趣故事；用巧妙的构思将大家带入奇妙的心理之旅；用扎实的绘画功底描绘出一幅幅精美的心灵王国；用暖人的色彩让心灵倍感温馨。此次活动，既传播了心理健康的精神，又丰富了校园心理健康文化，展示了我校学生积极正向的状态和风采，相信通过这样的活动心理健康的重要性会更加深入人心。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 37.33px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-top: 0px;text-indent: 42.66px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21.33px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">通过心理健康手抄报大赛，同学们对心理健康方面的知识更加深入了解，更懂得在学习和生活中将心理健康的光芒传递给身边的人，希望全体同学都能关心他人、助人自助、乐观向上，为建设和谐健康校园做出自己的贡献。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>					</p>', '0', '1525358352', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `dk_article` (`id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `subtitle`, `thumb`, `video`, `content`, `note`, `create_at`, `enabled`, `sort`, `click`, `istj`, `istwtj`, `link`) VALUES
(20, 9, '我校成功举办第三届素质拓展大赛', '', '', NULL, '<p>					</p><p><br/></p><p style="margin: 20.86px 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt;"><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体">我校成功举办</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt;"><span style="font-family:方正小标宋简体">第三届素质拓展大赛</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">“三月金明柳絮飞,岸花堤草弄春时”。</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">4</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">月</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">22</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">日</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">上午</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">，我校西北五环体育场素质拓展基地一片欢声笑语，来自全校</span>1</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">0</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">个院</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">系</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">）</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">的</span>168</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">名同学斗志昂扬、情绪高涨地参加了</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">以</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">“熔炼团队、超越自我”为主题的第</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">三</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">届素质拓展大赛。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">上午</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">8</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">时，开幕式准时举行。体育部副主任蔡寄平、体育教研室主任张亚廷、学生处心理健康教育科</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">科长</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">郭豪杰、校素质拓展指导老师</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">刘娟、</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">各参赛队伍指导老师出席开幕式并担任大赛团队展示环节评委。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">开幕式上，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">校素质拓展队的全体成员为大家带来了八段锦的表演</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">；</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">参赛代表刘汶泷</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">激情洋溢地发言，表示</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">将以积极、饱满、热情的态度参加本次比赛，胜不骄，败不馁</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">；</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">裁判组队长李志康带领裁判组宣誓：将以公平、公正、公开的原则执裁此次的比赛。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img title="1524875351929860.png" alt="image.png" src="/upload/image/2018-04-28/1524875351929860.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 21.1pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 21.1pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体">校素质拓展队表演</span>“八段锦”</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img title="1524875384217249.png" alt="image.png" src="/upload/image/2018-04-28/1524875384217249.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 21.1pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体">运动员代表发言</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 21.1pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体"></span></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">团队展示环节现场气氛热烈，</span>1</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">4</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">支参赛代表队激情昂扬、朝气蓬勃地展示了本队的队名、队旗、队形、队训和队歌等，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">充分展现了当代大学生良好的精神风貌。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img title="1524875416566519.png" alt="image.png" src="/upload/image/2018-04-28/1524875416566519.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 21.1pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 21.1pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体">代表队进行团队展示</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 21.1pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体"></span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">竞赛项目环节，参赛队伍限时挑战</span>“</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">十人九足</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">”、“无敌风火轮”、“</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">勇</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">跃硫酸池</span>”、“有轨电车”四个拓展项目</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">各院</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">系</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">）</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">代表队</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">团结合作，争分夺秒，竞争场面激烈，也引来了许多同学驻足观看，为他们加油助威。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">今年新增的</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">“十人九足”项目竞争激烈，参赛队伍被分</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">列</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">于起跑线的两端，每组的同学都蓄势待发</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">、</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">精神饱满，每组的队员脚脚相系</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">、</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">肩肩相抱，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">奔跑</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">中</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">体现</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">了</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">团结和</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">友谊</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">比赛中，同学们都表现出了极大的</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">热情和</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">顽强拼搏的</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">精神</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">，比赛场面激烈而友好。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 30pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img title="1524875455423731.png" alt="image.png" src="/upload/image/2018-04-28/1524875455423731.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体">项目一：有轨电车</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img title="1524875482367290.png" alt="image.png" src="/upload/image/2018-04-28/1524875482367290.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体">项目二：十人九足</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img title="1524875513916881.png" alt="image.png" src="/upload/image/2018-04-28/1524875513916881.png"/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"></span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"> </span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体">项目三：勇跃硫酸池</span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;<img title="1524875539297470.png" alt="image.png" src="/upload/image/2018-04-28/1524875539297470.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 30pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 28pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体">项目四：无敌风火轮</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 28pt;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:楷体"></span></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">团队分享环节每位参赛选手用一句话概括了此次大赛自己的感想和收获。经过激烈比拼，最终水利工程学院的</span>“什么都队”荣获了一等奖、水利工程学院的“对对队”、机械工程学院的“巅峰队”、管理系的“怼怼队”获得了二等奖，测绘工程学院的“开拓队”</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">等</span>8支队伍</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">获得了三等奖。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">本次活动</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">由学生工作</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">部（</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">处</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">）</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">主办，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">校阳光心理联合会和校素质拓展队联合承办。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">本次大赛</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">的</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">活动目的</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">是</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">为了宣传普及心理知识，丰富大学生的校园生活，绽放同学们的青春活力，拓展大学生个性潜力</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">提高大学生整体心理素质，培养大学生积极向上，合作互助的精神</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">比赛结束</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">后，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">一位参赛人员说：</span>“在本次的比赛中认识到很多朋友，</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">更</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">认识到团队精神和</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">团队</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">配合的重要性，对自己今后的工作有很大的帮助。</span>”</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">心理联合会主席</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">张金锋说：</span>“本次活动达到了预期的效果。希望通过这次活动能鼓励大学生在学习之余走出宿舍，增强自己的集体意识与责任意识，丰富自己的大学生活。”</span><span style="margin: 0px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt;"></span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>					</p>', '0', '1526614289', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, ''),
