e: 19px;">3月-4月</span></span></p></td><td width="323" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">微笑图片征集活动</span></span></p></td><td width="118" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">见附件2</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style="page-break-inside: avoid;"><td width="63" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext; padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">3</span></span></p></td><td width="126" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">3月-5月</span></span></p></td><td width="323" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">第八届心理主题班会评选活动</span></span></p></td><td width="118" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">见附件3</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style="page-break-inside: avoid;"><td width="63" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext; padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">4</span></span></p></td><td width="126" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">5月21-22日</span></span></p></td><td width="323" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">现场心理测评、现场心理咨询与沙盘展示活动</span></span></p></td><td width="118" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">青年大道</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style="page-break-inside: avoid;"><td width="63" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext; padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">5</span></span></p></td><td width="126" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">5月23日</span></span></p></td><td width="323" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">心理主题班会评选决赛</span></span></p></td><td width="118" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">学术报告厅</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style="page-break-inside: avoid;"><td width="63" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext; padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">6</span></span></p></td><td width="126" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">5月24日</span></span></p></td><td width="323" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">大学生自信风采大赛决赛</span></span></p></td><td width="118" valign="center" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">学生活动中心报告厅</span></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">四、活动要求</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">各系根据活动要求和本系实际情况，充分发挥班级心理委员的作用，积极参与，做好动员，大力推动心理素质教育深入开展，营造健康、和谐的校园心理文化氛围。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">五、组织单位</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">主办：学生处心理咨询中心</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">承办：大学生阳光心理联合会</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">附件：1. 关于开展心理素质拓展训练活动的通知</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">2. 关于开展微笑图片征集活动的通知</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">3. 关于开展第八届心理主题班会评选活动的通知</span></span></p><p style="text-align: right; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">2015年3月23日</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;"><br/></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">附件1</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family:;">关于开展心理素质拓展训练活动的通知</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">一、活动目的</span></strong><strong> </strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">心理咨询中心根据我院学生面临最多的环境适应、人际交往、情绪情感、压力管理、团体合作等问题，准备了一系列的素质拓展训练项目和方案，请各系在本学期根据本系实际需要和时间进行选择和预约。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">二、参与对象</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">各系决定活动参与人员名单，每次活动原则上不超过100人。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">三、活动流程</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">1.请各系提前与学生处（具体联系人见表1）预约素质拓展训练活动，并提交活动需求表（见表2）；</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">2.学生处制定活动方案，在系心理指导老师、系阳光心理联合分会的配合下，按照约定时间组织素质拓展活动；</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">3.活动结束后，各系对素质拓展活动进行总结，并及时提交活动通讯稿、活动照片、活动总结等相关资料，作为资料留存和系部心理健康教育工作考核依据。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">四、活动时间</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">2015年3月</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;">—</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">5月。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">五、活动地点</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">校园内部，具体地点根据活动方案需要确定。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">六、活动要求</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">1.请各系根据通知精神，广泛宣传、积极动员，做好素质拓展活动的预约、报名和组织工作；</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">2.请各系辅导员和心理指导老师积极参与，系阳光心理联合分会会长、各班心理委员和其他班干部积极配合，保证活动的顺利进行；</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 37px; text-indent: 48px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">3.请参加素质拓展活动的学生以运动装、运动鞋为主。严格听从现场老师的指导及遵守各项纪律要求。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px; font-weight: bold;"><br/></span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;">表1</span></span></p><p style="margin: 16px 0px; text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); letter-spacing: -1px; font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 24px;">素质拓展训练分组情况及联系表</span></span></p><table width="637"><tbody><tr class="firstRow" style="height: 54px; page-break-inside: avoid;"><td width="91" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border: 1px solid windowtext; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;">序 号</span></strong></span></p></td><td width="168" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;">联系系部</span></strong></span></p></td><td width="147" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px; background-color: transparent;"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(103, 106, 108); font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;">联系老师</span></strong></span></p></td><td width="147" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px 1px 1px 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; borde